對家叛國嘅資料。<br />\n<br />\n香港都有一堆人面對不義之事企出嚟變勇武，而本身戰鬥民族支持者，會唔會就咁算。"},{"pid":"0c5d8e3825862091136e34d14c723f28ac9e0143","tid":2278634,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3e4dfc75a82debaa0b7cf540580f4c22e9edc87","tid":2278634,"uid":224479,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"president XI果然夠老友 best friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"chairman xi先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a8f88d1357a27a76950a4eb0bbdcafeaab5cfa","tid":2278634,"uid":170229,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d8ffc8b4565e90824e244e6b8a0a296af6f8f724","tid":2278634,"uid":92230,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"左媒想突顯呢堆「敵對」國家無特別鐘意biden"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T13:55:56.000Z","msg":"其實正正係因為係敵國，所以會想出少句聲，廢事引火上身。靜雞睇美國人自爆咪算。"},{"pid":"baa21d1e60c9b44e51fcb5900ba6bee03aa8c015","tid":2278634,"uid":76331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b52f1ffe1776c4100e36c436d1ecc6ea12f07a","tid":2278634,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/business/status/1325722560634482688?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstatus%2F1325722560634482688%3Fs%3D21&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=31218a9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstatus%2F1325722560634482688%3Fs%3D21&h=e7eb1fc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/business/status/1325722560634482688?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nbloomberg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T1